channel.title: [BlakeScape]Project Osiris ~ 194 Look a like ~ The good old days
channel.description:
[img]http://img651.imageshack.us/img651/3296/osirisq.png[/img]
[b]This thread is about recreating a RS-2 Beta. This is not an attempt to make a RS-2 Beta remake, this is only a project I'm working on for fun. There's alot of work to be done, so wish me good luck.[/b]
[hr]
[b]READ: No, me and Native haven't quit the Project Osiris. This is released so people might find it useful. We started on a blank BlakeScape, we've done alot of work on it, and we had a good time doing this, even if it was hard, we actually made something out of it. We're going to swap on Hyperion. Why? Because the codes in this source are messy, needs alot of cleaning..[/b]
Thanks to Native, he has done alot of work, and got out working some awesome stuff.
So this are the server features:
[ul][li]Pickup (the pickup dupe needs to be fixed though)[/li] [li]Banking[/li] [li]Dropping[/li] [li]Leveling up[/li] [li]Leveling up interfaces, sending the correct chatbox interfaces and messages[/li] [li]Skill experience[/li] [li]Bones burying[/li] [li]Emotions[/li] [li]Graphics with almost all gfx's working[/li] [li]Animations with starting and stopping[/li] [li]Animations aren't being played for only 0.5 seconds, works perfectly[/li] [li]Game interfaces[/li] [li]Chat bar interface support[/li] [li]Item class supporting item and object creating[/li] [li]Textures renaming[/li] [li]A lovely welcome screen, old school one though[/li] [li]The client class has been cleaned alot[/li] [li]Woodcutting base, not finished[/li] [li]NPC system implemented[/li] [li]Running has to be fixed[/li] [li]The beard needs a fix[/li][/ul] Client features:
[ul][li]319 cache[/li] [li]194 gameframe[/li] [li]194 textures[/li] [li]289 items[/li] [li]289 npcs[/li] [li]nearly all 194 media[/li][/ul] Note: I've done nothing with the client, so 100% credits to Purely chill from the R-S community. [hr] Media:
[img]http://img207.imageshack.us/img207/203/loginscreen.png[/img]
[img]http://img717.imageshack.us/img717/7613/194fally.png[/img]
Leveling up [img]http://img835.imageshack.us/img835/3273/levelingup.png[/img]
Bones burying [img]http://img97.imageshack.us/img97/6917/bonesburying.png[/img]
Emotions :D [img]http://img97.imageshack.us/img97/2016/emotions.png[/img]
Leveling with interfaces [img]http://img571.imageshack.us/img571/3273/levelingup.png[/img]
